[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces" css=".vc_custom_1499060433376{background-color: #f6f6f7 !important;}" el_class="about-top-txt"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="91" img_size="full"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" el_class="row-flex-text"][vc_column_text el_class="col-50 ab-pages"]

More than 10 years of cleaning experience

Cleaning Company service is a fully integrated janitorial cleaning services company that provides comprehensive, high quality, reliable cleaning solutions to commercial, corporate, industrial and residential clients. Our diligent management and work ethic are central to Cleaning Company service business philosophy and critical to delivering consistent, quality cleaning services. We pride ourselves on making our management accountable to the client through direct access and interaction with our managing director.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space height="50px"][cleaning_services_icon_hor col_no="2"][cleaning_services_icon_hor_items icon="icon-target-lined" heading="Our Mission"]Aims to be a national market leader in the provision of cleaning services delivering reliable, quality, cost effective cleaning solutions to our customers[/cleaning_services_icon_hor_items][cleaning_services_icon_hor_items icon="icon-brush-lined" heading="Our Vision"]We have more than 215 franchise locations across the United States and Canada. If you’re not happy, just let us know and we’ll work to make it right

[/vc_column_text][cleaning_sevice_action_button title="Just Contact us" call_action="url:http%3A%2F%2Fsmartdata.tonytemplates.com%2Fcleaning-service%2Fcontacts%2F|||" icon="icon-technology" extra_class="about-pages-btn btn-white"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1506935343627{padding-bottom: 60px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Our Team

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

Cleaning Company is a minority owned business with a large group of specially trained, dedicated employees to provide professional service with a personal touch.

[/vc_column_text][cleaning_services_team_carousel][cleaning_services_team name="Alan Yarbrough" designation="Managing Director" image="109"]

Alan started in 1985 and provides the leadership needed to maintain our reputation and goodwill in the community.

[/cleaning_services_team][cleaning_services_team name="Wilford Wood" designation="Customer Service Manager" image="110"]He is the direct “pipeline” to our customers to ensure they are being heard and their special needs are being met.[/cleaning_services_team][cleaning_services_team name="Teresa Phillips" designation="Office Administrator" image="111"]Teresa joined our team in 2009. She brings a wealth of knowledge and experience in the accounting field.[/cleaning_services_team][/cleaning_services_team_carousel][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Our Values

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

Our goal is Your satisfaction (of course after our cleaning work). Office Phone works around the clock (24/7).

[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner el_class="value-area"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="92" img_size="full"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
  • Client oriented: We serve our clients as if we were serving ourselves. We value their feedback and we use it to improve our work.
  • Eco-Friendly Oriented: We carefully choose the best and most natural cleaning products that give amazing results.
  • Excellence and Innovation: We provide training to our personnel in order to ensure the high standard of service. We stay up-to-date on the latest innovations in eco-friendly products and technologies, allowing us to bring the best in to our clients’ homes.
  • Expansion / Growth: we make ourselves known in the community; we create long term relations, while constantly expanding. Therefore, we are always bringing in more people to work for us.
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1498114056290{padding-top: 80px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]

History of Cleaning Company

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

Providing house and offices cleaning services for more nhan 10 years

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

The Cleaning Company is widely recognized for our commitment to serving our customers while staying friendly to the environment. We have a history of excellence and dedication to our clients, providing professional and high-quality house cleaning services across America.

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

Franchising began in 1996 and has grown to include more than 215 locations across North America.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]Our company was founded in the Baltimore- Washington metro area in 1987 as one of the first whole house cleaning services in the region. In 1989, Martin Greg and John Rambo purchased the company and broadened its scope to serve even more clients.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]This quality commitment and reputation for excellent service attracted outside investors. In 2014, the company announced a majority acquisition by PNC Riverarch Capital. This exciting change didn't mean a complete overhaul:[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]The management team did not change and Steve continued on in his leadership position with the Board of Directors. We are excited to announce a new era of growth for both new and existing units under the guidance of PNC.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1498114378108{margin-top: 60px !important;margin-bottom: 80px !important;}"][vc_column][cleaning_services_guarantee_banner title="Satisfaction Guaranteed!" image="93"]Your satisfaction is 100% guaranteed at Cleaning Company. If you are not happy with any area we’ve cleaned, simply call within 24 hours and we will come back out and reclean it free of charge. This makes hiring Cleaning Company virtually risk free. Our maids are thoroughly screened through our rigorous recruitment process, and every one of them goes through our Maid University training process.[/cleaning_services_guarantee_banner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]

Why Hire Us?

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]

Choose us because of our reputation for excellence. For more than 10 years, we've earned a name for quality and customer service. The homeowners we serve rely on us for detail-oriented, consistent cleaning services, every single time we clean their homes.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1506592745251{padding-top: 20px !important;}" el_class="about-pages-23"][vc_column][cleaning_services_carousel_box col_no="3"][cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items icon="icon-like-lined" heading="With Us, Your Satisfaction Is Guaranteed"]The experts at The Cleaning Company are committed to providing thorough house cleaning services for our valued customers nationwide. In order to accomplish this goal, we adhere to strict standards that remain consistent across the board.[/cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items][cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items icon="icon-user-lined" heading="Our Bonded & Insured Cleaning Team"]Our company is fully bonded and insured, which means you can have peace of mind when you hire us as your residential cleaning company. Helping our customers feel confident in our services is very important to us.[/cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items][cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items icon="icon-users-lined" heading="Our Teams Consist of Fully Trained Employees"]It means every individual hired at a franchise location of Cleaning Company goes through a thorough screening process, and then is trained in every aspect of our home cleaning services. This ensures high-quality service every time.[/cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items][cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items icon="icon-map-lined" heading="Locally Owned Home Cleaning Services"]Life is just too short to clean your own home. You should be able to enjoy peace of mind knowing that your home is in good hands, while focusing on things that matter more to you, such as your family and loved ones.[/cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items][cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items icon="icon-reward-lined" heading="Free Over the Phone Estimates"]Cleaning Company service is the key to keeping a beautiful home while making more time for yourself and the things you love most. Contact us for a FREE estimate.[/cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items][cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items icon="icon-like-lined" heading="We Guarantee Our Work"]Cleaning Company strives to provide the highest level of quality, service and value to each and every customer. If you are not completely satisfied with our service, please inform us within 24 hours of your clean so we may resolve the situation.[/cleaning_services_icon_carousel_items][/cleaning_services_carousel_box][/vc_column][/vc_row]

item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
"I am still learning about my home. If you can't do it yourself, find good service people and treat them well." — Terry (mom to our Human Resources Coordinator, Louisa)
Raise your hand if you grew up with a mom (or another parental figure) constantly reminding you to clean your room. Often, our earliest memories of figuring out how to tidy up and take care of our homes are with our moms—they taught us how to do laundry, how to do the dishes, and how to make our beds. So it should come as no surprise that when we asked our moms for their best homekeeping advice, they came back with some great tips. Most agreed on a few major themes: it's important to make sure everything has a home, that you put things back when you take them out, and that your home is an inviting, relaxing place to come home to—and invite others to.

Raise your hand if you grew up with a mom (or another parental figure) constantly reminding you to clean your room. So it should come as no surprise that when we asked our moms for their best homekeeping advice, they came back with some great tips.
